   {
      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "`scriptPubKey` has like `dummyText` no affect in `createrawtransaction` inputs\n\nThe code only parses `txid` and `vout`: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/src/rpcrawtransaction.cpp#L358\n\nExample:\n\n```\njonasschnelli$ ./src/bitcoin-cli --regtest createrawtransaction '[{\"txid\":\"20155e5341155abdbc0b9f4965f206c2b5c61075bcb46d65645efe7c9ea932f9\",\"vout\":0, \"ScriptPubKey\":\"a91407694cfd2bd43f4e0fe285a4d013456cb58d7eab87\", \"alice\":\"is bob\"}]' '{\"miBMjNNiy5eR9UZV69GzMiapa7Hsiyib51\" : 0.042}'\n0100000001f932a99e7cfe5e64656db4bc7510c6b5c206f265499f0bbcbd5a1541535e15200000000000ffffffff0140164000000000001976a9141d339f3499cdbeccbc8c7d30c122775923cb612288ac00000000\n\njonasschnelli$ ./src/bitcoin-cli --regtest createrawtransaction '[{\"txid\":\"20155e5341155abdbc0b9f4965f206c2b5c61075bcb46d65645efe7c9ea932f9\",\"vout\":0, \"scriptPubKey\":\"a91407694cfd2bd43f4e0fe285a4d013456cb58d7eab87\", \"alice\":\"is bob\"}]' '{\"miBMjNNiy5eR9UZV69GzMiapa7Hsiyib51\" : 0.042}'\n0100000001f932a99e7cfe5e64656db4bc7510c6b5c206f265499f0bbcbd5a1541535e15200000000000ffffffff0140164000000000001976a9141d339f3499cdbeccbc8c7d30c122775923cb612288ac00000000\n```\n",
